228, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"the youngsters\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Delandro has ambitious plans to become a bit of a guru at the end of the five-day crash course.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Delandro\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"ambitious plans\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"a guru\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"the five-day crash course\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am trying to be like an ambassador for bocce.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an ambassador\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"bocce\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I go back to St Lucia I want to pass on what I learn to other teachers so we can even go into other schools that are inclusive,\\\" she told theObserver.\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2472, \"end\": 2480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999245119, \"rank\": 7.533777152322978e-11, \"text\": \"St Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other teachers\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"other schools\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"theObserver\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had been reading and watching videos, but\\u2026 now that I am here I am getting a more practical view of what it's really like.\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"a more practical view\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"