andard of coaching and officiating.\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the knock-on effect\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"the standard\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3106}, {\"ngram\": \"coaching\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We just want to maintain the game being played under proper rules.\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3171}, {\"ngram\": \"proper rules\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like any sport, when you do not remember anything about the officials there is a reason for that - the game went like it was supposed to.\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any sport\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3219}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3254}, {\"ngram\": \"the officials\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"a reason\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There wasn't a fiasco, there wasn't a rule interpretation that was wrong.\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fiasco\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3364}, {\"ngram\": \"a rule interpretation\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of that goes back to the coaches understanding what we want as officials, and also the players understanding what the coaches want.\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"the coaches\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3457}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3497}, {\"ngram\": \"also the players\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3519}, {\"ngram\": \"the coaches\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The athletes who have had a certain level of coaching can maintain the 